  </intervention>
  <eligibility>
    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  bilaterally symmetric extraction of premolar teeth with residual extraction spaces
             large enough to ensure space closure is not complete prior to the subsequent
             orthodontic appointment

          -  no medicines or systemic illness

          -  full banding/bonding of teeth

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  pregnant

          -  non-extraction treatment

          -  systemic illness

          -  prior orthodontic treatment
      </textblock>
    </criteria>
